## Local LLM Fallback Testing

```python
@pytest.mark.asyncio
async def test_local_llm_fallback(client: AsyncClient, mock_openrouter_offline):
    """System falls back to local LLM when OpenRouter is unavailable."""
    response = await client.post("/api/v1/briefing/generate")
    data = response.json()

    assert data["status"] == "success"
    assert "local" in data["metadata"]["model_used"].lower()
