## CI/CD Integration

### GitHub Actions Test Stage
```yaml
test:
  runs-on: ubuntu-latest
  steps:
    - uses: actions/checkout@v4
    - uses: astral-sh/setup-uv@v4
    - run: uv sync --frozen
    - run: uv run pytest --cov=backend --cov-report=xml
    - run: npm ci --prefix frontend
    - run: npm run test --prefix frontend -- --coverage
```

### Coverage Gates
- Backend: 80% line coverage minimum
- Frontend: 75% line coverage minimum
- Security tests: 100% of OWASP matrix must pass
- No PR merge without passing security test suite

