- [ ] All `test_requirements` from task JSON implemented
- [ ] Backend coverage >= 80%
- [ ] Frontend coverage >= 75%
- [ ] Security tests pass (all OWASP vectors)
- [ ] Test suite inventory current (`test_suite_inventory.py` passes if tests added/removed)
- [ ] Injection corpus inventory current (`test_corpus_inventory.py` passes if payloads/patterns changed)
- [ ] No skipped tests without documented reason
- [ ] CI pipeline passes

